{"tid":2386180,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"粉嶺公屋母女疑新年自行印新鈔 打印機印製閃粉筆畫金屬線","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:15:50.000Z","uid":230530,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28af3875dfffda2fa6738349946c75af09fe9fd8","tid":2386180,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"粉嶺一對母女疑於華明邨住所，使用噴墨打印機印製偽鈔，並以閃粉筆塗上偽鈔偽裝成金屬線，用以模仿真鈔防偽特徵。警方昨日（28日）採取行動，於旺角染布房街截查一名43歲女子，於其身上搜出7張面額500元偽鈔，其後再於其粉嶺華明邨寓所起出一批偽鈔及打印機、閃粉筆等工具。涉事43歲女子及其22歲女兒被警方以「製造偽製紙幣」等罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n以打印機加閃粉筆自製偽鈔 主要於新界街市食肆發現<br />\n<br />\n商業罪案調查科高級督察鄧國軒交代案情指，警方自去年12月起已留意到有一批質素低劣之偽鈔流入市面，偽鈔面額由20至500元不等，主要在新界區的街市、麵包店及食肆等小商戶發現。警方透過翻查閉路電視鎖定一名女子，在昨日於旺角將疑犯拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方將女子押返粉嶺華明邨寓所，於單位內起出一批面值共2.35萬元的500元面值偽鈔，另外尚有一套製造偽鈔工具，包括家用式噴墨打印機、多枝閃粉顏色筆、顏料、間尺、𠝹刀等等。探員同時在單位發現女子的22歲女兒，二人涉嫌「製造偽製紙幣」、「管有偽製紙幣」、「行使偽製紙幣」等罪名，警方指不排除會有更多人士被捕。<br />\n<br />\n偽鈔質素低劣不難分辨<br />\n<br />\n鄧國軒又指該批偽鈔只得2組序號，均是用家用式噴墨打印機印製，開窗式金屬線亦是以閃粉筆塗上，其製作質素低劣，與真鈔有明顯分別，市民只需小心觀察即容易分辨。"},{"pid":"e3e80342cf57be8bbe1511ace8e09266f5d5cd32","tid":2386180,"uid":202541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"低質都冇人發現嗰下好笑"},{"pid":"e60d860c90a71c0b8f22e209d2e13fd9a2c3c345","tid":2386180,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">於旺角染布房街截查一名43歲女子，於其身上搜出7張面額500元偽鈔</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/thumb/7/77/%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E9%AC%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93.jpg/250px-%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E9%AC%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F7%2F77%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%25AC%25BC%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593.jpg%2F250px-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%25AC%25BC%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593.jpg&h=b62a8e3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1c277be2631a84e4b75697952ef6eaf290cd14e","tid":2386180,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"摸上手會唔知？"},{"pid":"c736997b04dd622a79113fc62ebfc8e5f7d520c8","tid":2386180,"uid":326140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:10:24.000Z","msg":"智障會遺傳"},{"pid":"f509bb51e4180d9692894c19c64dcccd88195b8a","tid":2386180,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1c277be2631a84e4b75697952ef6eaf290cd14e","tid":2386180,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"摸上手會唔知？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"比食錢機食左都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea58cd5f9142b3db19d43ad2c1c1c2ef918787d","tid":2386180,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你窮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282b8aa022aa3d12bf6c76afbb558934a23e25fb","tid":2386180,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c736997b04dd622a79113fc62ebfc8e5f7d520c8","tid":2386180,"uid":326140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:10:24.000Z","msg":"智障會遺傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432d992b9d21f9937e989894f94d8fad54515f59","tid":2386180,"uid":375148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"普通a4?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3227c30f7d37454c1e163ce03575b9d0c162d48b","tid":2386180,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0